c: 59
v: 18
t: "ya 'ayuha aladhin sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu bshreh, khafuu allh, wahdharuu eqabh bifiel ma 'amrakum bih wtrk ma nahakum enh, wlttdbr kulu nafs maa qadamat min al'aemal liawm alqyamt, wkhafu allah fi kl ma tatwn wama tadharwn, 'iina allah subhanah khabir bima temlwn, la yakhfaa ealayh shay' min aemalkm, wahu mjazykm elyha"